ard to cancel up to 5 damage just dealt to a character.',NULL,0,'2',NULL,0,0,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Owen William Weber','7a8f5eb3-4c89-4516-974b-812b589cb818','2016-03-14 23:12:58','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10004.png'),(379,30,3,1,5,'10005','Raven-winged Helm','Item. Armor.','Attach a hero with Sentinel. Limit 1 per hero.\n<b>Response:</b> Exhaust Raven-winged Helm to prevent 1 point of damage just dealt to attached character.','He had a small hauberk, its rings of forged of steel, maybe, yet black as jet; and a high-crowned helm with small raven-wings on either side, set with a silver star in the centre of the circlet.\n<cite>The Return of the King</cite>',0,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Blake Henriksen','62dd5a22-ccf4-4612-be1f-ea13d7da3ced','2016-03-14 23:13:20','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10005.png'),(380,30,2,2,6,'10006','Curious Brandybuck','Hobbit.','<b>Forced:</b> After the active location is explored, place Curious Brandybuck on the bottom of its owner\'s deck.\n<b>Response:</b> After you travel to a location, put Curious Brandybuck into play from your hand, under any player\'s control.','',0,'2',NULL,2,0,0,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Matthew Starbuck','c52c00b2-ab39-4ffa-898d-ab9c8246bd00','2016-03-14 23:13:47','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10006.png'),(381,30,3,2,7,'10007','Hobbit Pony','Mount.','Attach to a <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> hero. Restricted.\r\n<b>Quest Action:</b> If attached hero is not committed to the quest, exhaust Hobbit Pony and attached hero to commit attached hero to the quest.','He was riding a pony, and a scarf was swathed round his neck and over his chin to keep out the fog.\r\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Eva Maria Toker','ebcb133a-1777-49cf-a7d4-137a65b2c2d5','2016-03-14 23:14:17','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10007.png'),(382,30,2,4,8,'10008','East Road Ranger','Dúnedain. Scout.','East Road Ranger gets +2 [willpower] while committed t