-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10028.png'),(386,31,2,3,29,'10029','Veteran of Osgiliath','Gondor. Warrior.','Veteran of Osgiliath gets +1 [willpower], +1 [attack], and +1 [defense] while your threat is 40 or higher.','\"So do we ever watch the shores nigh Osgiliath, which our enemies now partly hold, and issue from it to harry our lands.\"\n<cite>Faramir, The Two Towers</cite>',0,'3',NULL,1,2,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'John Stanko','0484e428-6a72-4841-b2d5-d8df7cfb51bf','2016-03-14 23:18:20','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10029.png'),(387,31,4,3,30,'10030','Descendants of Kings',NULL,'Ready up to X <b><i>Dúnedain</i></b> characters you control. X is the number of enemies engaged with you.','\"But when dark things come from the houseless hills, or creep from sunless woods, they fly from us.\"\r\n<cite>Aragorn, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Smirtouille','25641d97-e196-40d5-8481-727602aa2da2','2016-03-14 23:18:44','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10030.png'),(388,31,2,1,31,'10031','Derndingle Warrior','Ent. Warrior.','Sentinel.\r\nCannot have restricted attachments.\r\nEnters play exhausted.\r\nWhile Derndingle Warrior is defending, it gains: \"<b>Action:</b> Deal 1 damage to Derndingle Warrior to give it +3 [defense] for this attack.\" (Limit once per attack.)',NULL,0,'2',NULL,1,1,2,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Oscar RÃ¶mer','e562d744-bf7d-4325-97ba-424bf3ca3ca8','2016-03-14 23:19:31','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/10031.png'),(389,31,4,1,32,'10032','Boomed and Trumpeted','Ent.','<b>Response:</b> After an <b><i>Ent</i></b> character takes any amount of damage, ready it. That character gets +3 [attack] until the end of the phase.','\"They roared and boomed and trumpeted, until stones began to crack and fall at the mere noise of them.\" <cite>Merry, The Two Towers</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Jordan Saia','f4b2af17-b589-49c1-a884-ecd4570d8545','2016-03-14 23:28:51','2025-10-16 14:24:15'