a location in the staging area. Shuffle the encounter deck.','',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Lucas Durham','fe1a0aef-10bd-441b-a27b-0527810fef57','2016-03-15 00:47:05','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/11008.png'),(443,36,2,4,9,'11009','Lindon Navigator','Noldor. Scout.','Lindon Navigator does not exhaust to commit to a quest, and can commit to quests while exhausted.\n<b>Forced:</b> After resolving a quest to which Lindon Navigator was committed, either discard it from play or discard 1 card from your hand.','',0,'2',NULL,2,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Tiziano Baracchi','a09013c9-0eeb-459d-b7fc-d803d1b0ad1d','2016-03-15 00:47:14','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/11009.png'),(444,36,4,4,10,'11010','The Evening Star','','<b>Action:</b> Place 2 progress on any location. Resolve that effect again for each copy of The Evening Star currently in your discard pile (you may choose new targets).','...for ever still a herald on\nan errand that should never rest\nto bear his shining lamp afar,\nthe Flammifer of Westernesse.\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Katy Grierson','b6729381-3bfc-41fa-abd1-99f410eb19b8','2016-03-15 00:47:23','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/11010.png'),(445,36,3,4,11,'11011','Explorer\'s Almanac','Item.','Attach to a location in the staging area.\nProgress from questing successfully may be placed on the attached location before it is placed on the current quest.','',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Ed Mattinian','21f0acdb-5d11-409e-80f8-c717fab87ab9','2016-03-15 00:47:34','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/11011.png'),(446,36,2,2,12,'11012','Sailor of Lune','Noldor. Scout.','While the top card of your discard pile is an event, Sailor of Lune gets +1 [willpower] and gains: \"Cannot be damaged while committed to the quest.\"','\"They are sailing, sailing, sailing over the Sea, they are going into the West and leaving us,\" said Sam, half chanting the words, shaking his head sadly and solemnly.\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'2',NULL,1,1,0,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Owen William Weber','85a269eb-63f1-4f63-83c9-30b718d364f6','2016-03-15 00:47:53','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/11012.png'),(447,36,4,2,13,'11013','Elwing\'s Flight','','<b>Quest Action:</b> Ready a questing character and give that character +1 [willpower] until the end of the phase. Resolve that effect again for each copy of Elwing\'s Flight currently in your discard pile (you may choose different targets).','There flying Elwing came to him\nand flame was in the darkness lit;\nmore bright than light of diamond\nthe fire upon her carcanet.\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'A. M. Sartor','d25dfbee-85c4-42f8-9653-c0536d3e5095','2016-03-15 00:48:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/11013.png'),(448,36,3,2,14,'11014','To the Sea, to the Sea!','Song.','Attach to a <b><i>Noldor</i></b> character.\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust To the Sea, to the Sea! and discard X cards from your hand to reduce the cost of the next <b><i>Noldor</i></b> ally played this phase by X (to a minimum of 1).','To the Sea, to the Sea! The white gulls are crying,\nThe wind is blowing, and the white foam is flying.\n<cite>The Return of the King</cite>',1,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Tawny Fritzinger','d0180ea8-15e3-4a9a-80c6-dfd6549753c9','2016-03-15 00:48:19','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/11014.png'),(449,36,3,5,15,'11015','Narya','Ring. Artifact.','Attach to Círdan the Shipwright or Gandalf.\r\nAttached character gains a [leadership] resource icon. \r\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Narya and attached character to choose and ready up to 2 allies. Each of those allies gets +1 [attack] and +1 [defense] until the end of the phase.','\"For this is the Ring of Fire, and with it you may rekindle hearts in a world that grows chill.\"\r\n<cite>Círdan, The Return of the King</cite>',1,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,N