ot exhaust to defend.','The roar of his voice was like drums and guns; and he tossed wolves and goblins from his path like straws and feathers.\n<cite>The Hobbit</cite>',1,NULL,12,0,5,1,10,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Emrah Elmasli','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9015','2016-03-17 00:17:18','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131005.png'),(455,37,2,3,6,'131006','Fili','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> After you play Fili from your hand during the planning phase, search your deck for Kili and put him into play under your control. Then, shuffle your deck.','\"Fili is the youngest and still has the best sight\" —Thorin, The Hobbit',1,'3',NULL,1,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Carmen Cianelti','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9032','2016-03-17 00:17:26','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131006.png'),(456,37,2,2,7,'131007','Kili','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> After you play Kili from your hand during the planning phase, search your deck for Fili and put him into play under your control. Then, shuffle your deck.','\"Let us join the throng!\" —Kili, The Hobbit',1,'3',NULL,1,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Carmen Cianelti','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9055','2016-03-17 00:17:32','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131007.png'),(457,37,2,1,8,'131008','Bofur','Dwarf.','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Bofur to search the top 5 cards of your deck for 1 <b><i>Weapon</i></b> attachment. Add that card to your hand and shuffle the other cards back into your deck.','',1,'3',NULL,2,2,0,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'David A. Nash','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9019','2016-03-17 00:17:37','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131008.png'),(458,37,2,4,9,'131009','Dori','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> After a hero is assigned any amount of damage, exhaust Dori to place that damage on Dori instead.','',1,'3',NULL,1,2,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Jake Murray','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9027','2016-03-17 00:18:47','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131009.png'),(459,37,2,5,10,'131010','Gandalf','Istari.','Gandalf does not exhaust to commit to a quest.\n<b>Forced:</b> At the end of the refresh phase, discard Gandalf from play. You may raise your threat by 2 to cancel this effect.','',1,'5',NULL,4,4,4,4,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9036','2016-03-17 00:19:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131010.png'),(460,37,3,3,11,'131011','Cram','Item.','Attach to a hero.\n<b>Action:</b> Discard Cram to ready attached hero.','',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Adam Lane','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9024','2016-03-17 00:19:34','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131011.png'),(461,37,3,2,12,'131012','Spare Hood and Cloak','Item.','Attach to a character.\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Spare Hood and Cloak and exhaust attached character to ready another character. Then, attach Spare Hood and Cloak to that character.','\"You will have to manage without pocket-handkerchiefs, and a good many other things, before you get to the journey\'s end. As for a hat, I have got a spare hood and cloak in my luggage.\" <cite>Dwalin, The Hobbit</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'David Kegg','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9074','2016-03-17 00:19:49','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131012.png'),(462,37,3,4,13,'131013','Thrór\'s Map','Artifact. Item.','Attach to a hero.\r\n<b>Travel Action:</b> Discard Thrór\'s Map to choose a location in the staging area. Make that location the active location. (If there is another active location, return it to the staging area.)','\'This was made by Thrór, your grandfather, Thorin.\' he said in answer to the dwarves\' excited questions. \'It is a plan of the Mountain.\' <cite>Gandalf, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Jake Murray','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9084','2016-03-17 00:20:33','2025-10-16 14:24:15',1,'/bundles/cards/131013.png'),(463,37,4,3,14,'131014','A Very Good Tale','','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust 2 allies you control to shuffle your deck and discard the top 5 cards. Put up to 2 allies discarded by this effect into play under your control. The total cost of the allies put into play cannot exceed the total cost of the allies exhausted to pay for this effect.','',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9011','2016-03-17 00:20:48','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131014.png'),(464,37,4,1,15,'131015','Foe-hammer','','<b>Response:</b> After a hero you control attacks and destroys an enemy, exhaust a <b><i>Weapon</i></b> card attached to that hero to draw 3 cards.','',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9033','2016-03-17 00:20:58','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131015.png'),(465,37,4,1,16,'131016','Goblin-cleaver',NULL,'<b>Combat Action:</b> Exhaust a <b><i>Weapon</i></b> card attached to a hero you control to choose an enemy engaged with you. Deal 2 damage to that enemy. (Deal 3 damage instead if the enemy is an<b><i> Orc</i></b>.)','At this point Gandalf fell behind, and Thorin with him. They turned a sharp corner. \'About turn!\' he shouted. \'Draw your sword, Thorin!\' <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9043','2016-03-17 00:21:23','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131016.png'),(466,37,4,2,17,'131017','Late Adventurer','','<b>Quest Action:</b> Exhaust a character you control that is not committed to the quest to commit that character to the quest.','To the end of his days Bilbo could never remember how he found himself outside, without a hat, walking-stick or any money, or anything that he usually took when he went out. <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Carmen Cianelti','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9057','2016-03-17 00:21:38','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131017.png'),(467,37,4,4,18,'131018','Expecting Mischief','','Play during the quest phase, before the staging step.\n<b>Action:</b> Deal 2 damage to the first enemy revealed from the encounter deck this phase.','',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Ilich Henriquez','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9031','2016-03-17 00:21:59','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131018.png'),(468,37,4,6,19,'131019','Burglar Baggins',NULL,'<b>Action:</b> Bilbo Baggins gets +2 [willpower], +2 [attack], and +2 [defense] until the end of the phase. (You may spend a [baggins] resource from Bilbo Baggins\' resource pool to play this card even if you do not control Bilbo Baggins.)',NULL,0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Emrah Elmasli','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9020','2016-03-17 00:22:20','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131019.png'),(469,37,5,5,20,'131020','Sting','Artifact. Item. Weapon.','Attach to Bilbo Baggins. Restricted.\r\nBilbo Baggins gets +1 [willpower], +1 [attack], and +1 [defense].\r\n<b>Response:</b> After Bilbo Baggins exhausts to defend, discard the top card of the encounter deck. Deal damage to the attacking enemy equal to the discarded card\'s [threat].','\"I shall call you Sting.\" <cite>Bilbo, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Magali Villeneuve','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9075','2016-03-17 00:23:00','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131020.png'),(470,37,5,5,21,'131021','Orcrist','Artifact. Item. Weapon.','Attach to a hero. Restricted.\r\nAttached character gets +2 [attack].\r\n<b>Response:</b> After attached hero destroys an Orc enemy, add 1 resource to that hero\'s resource pool.','\"This, Thorin, the runes name Orcrist, the Goblin-cleaver in the ancient tongue of Gondolin; it was a famous blade.\" <cite>Elrond, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Magali Villeneuve','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9064','2016-03-17 00:23:13','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131021.png'),(471,37,5,5,22,'131022','Glamdring','Artifact. Item. Weapon.','Attach to a hero or Gandalf. Restricted.\r\nAttached character gets +2 [attack].\r\n<b>Response:</b> After attached character destroys an <b><i>Orc</i></b> enemy, draw 1 card.','\"This, Gandalf, was Glamdring, Foe-hammer that the king of Gondolin once wore.\" ―Elrond, The Hobbit',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Magali Villeneuve','51223bd0-ffd1-11df-a976-1801204c9037','2016-03-17 00:23:25','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/131022.png'),(472,38,1,6,1,'132001','Bilbo Baggins','Hobbit. Burglar.','Bilbo Baggins does not count against the hero limit and cannot gain resources from non-treasure cards. The first player gains control of Bilbo Baggins.\r\n<b>Action:</b> Spend 1 [baggins] resource to search your deck for a treasure card and add it to your hand.\r\n<b>If Bilbo Baggins leaves play, the players have lost the game.</b>',NULL,1,NULL,0,1,1,1,3,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Magali Villeneuve','4e61b160-2104-497f-9977-4b353e54fbb7','2016-03-17 00:30:49','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132001.png'),(473,38,1,3,2,'132002','Balin','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> Pay 1 resource from Balin\'s resource pool to cancel a shadow effect just triggered during an attack. Then, deal the attacking enemy another shadow card. (Limit once per attack.)','\"Well, it is the first time that even a mouse has crept along carefully and quietly under my very nose and not been spotted.\" <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',1,NULL,9,2,1,2,4,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Winona Nelson','bf2cb5a8-2ec6-4366-89f6-7e3010686a85','2016-03-17 00:32:36','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132002.png'),(474,38,1,1,3,'132003','Bard the Bowman','Esgaroth. Warrior.','Ranged.\nWhen Bard the Bowman makes a ranged attack, the enemy he attacks gets -2 [defense] until the end of the phase.','Now he shot with a great yew bow, till all his arrows but one were spent. <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',1,NULL,11,2,3,2,4,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Magali Villeneuve','e2cf87be-ccdc-48e9-8127-57bee67d4a0c','2016-03-17 00:32:42','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132003.png'),(475,38,1,2,4,'132004','Óin','Dwarf.','While you control at least 5 <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> characters, Óin gets +1 [attack] and gains the [tactics] resource icon.','Dwarves can make fire almost anywhere out of almost anything, wind or no wind... <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',1,NULL,8,2,1,1,4,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Jeff Lee Johnson','b21a2af5-7443-4630-9503-1b334ae51c6e','2016-03-17 00:32:48','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132004.png'),(476,38,1,4,5,'132005','Bombur','Dwarf.','When counting the number of <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> characters you control, Bombur counts as two.','\"Bombur is fattest and will do for two, he had better come alone and last.\" <cite>Gandalf, The Hobbit</cite>',1,NULL,8,0,1,2,5,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Ilich Henriquez','66f66c2e-36e7-4d97-aebb-1ca413f9edeb','2016-03-17 00:32:52','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132005.png'),(477,38,2,3,6,'132006','Glóin','Dwarf.','While you control at least 5 <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> characters, Glóin gains: \"<b>Response:</b> After you play Glóin from your hand, choose a hero. Add 2 resources to that hero\'s resource pool.\"','Glóin lit several more torches, and then they all crept out, one by one... <cite> The Hobbit </cite>',1,'3',NULL,2,1,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Jeff Lee Johnson','6778eb01-6b07-4dbe-87f1-e854ab548813','2016-03-17 00:32:57','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132006.png'),(478,38,2,4,7,'132007','Bifur','Dwarf.','While you control at least 5 <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> characters, Bifur gains: \"<b>Response:</b> After you play Bifur from your hand, draw 2 cards.\"','\"My cousins! Bombur and Bofur <cite> we have forgotten them, they are down in the valley!\" –The Hobbit</cite>',1,'3',NULL,1,2,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Taylor Ingvarsson','c4b959f5-92a9-4f46-8656-f9da08a5cb86','2016-03-17 00:33:07','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132007.png'),(479,38,2,2,8,'132008','Dwalin','Dwarf.','Sentinel.\r\nWhile you control at least 5 <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> characters, lower the cost to play Dwalin by 2.','As soon as the door was opened, he pushed inside, just as if he had been expected. –The Hobbit',1,'3',NULL,1,1,2,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Melanie Maier','c66638a7-95ae-4913-bf11-2e8dcf8d6104','2016-03-17 00:34:14','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132008.png'),(480,38,4,1,9,'132009','Straight Shot','','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust a <b><i>Weapon</i></b> attachment to choose a non-unique enemy with 0 [defense]. Discard the chosen enemy.','In it smote and vanished, barb, shaft and feather, so fierce was its flight. <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Ilich Henriquez','c2a79823-e4f9-4449-b467-5916d7e58979','2016-03-17 00:34:24','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132009.png'),(481,38,4,2,10,'132010','Desperate Alliance','','<b>Action:</b> Choose a hero you control. Until the end of the phase, give control of that hero and all resources in that hero\'s resource pool to another player. (Limit 1 per phase.)','\"Come!\" called Gandalf. \"There is yet time for council.\" <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','7465c18b-440e-4a90-8ac0-c50c0de03b5d','2016-03-17 00:34:30','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132010.png'),(482,38,4,4,11,'132011','Ravens of the Mountain',NULL,'<b>Action:</b> Exhaust a hero you control to shuffle the encounter deck and look at its top card. Place progress tokens on the current quest equal to the [threat] of the card you looked at. Then, put that card back on top of the encounter deck.','As they worked the ravens brought them constant tidings. <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Adam Lane','6d442a61-e9e9-4729-bac1-da3d76af6afa','2016-03-17 00:34:37','2025-10-16 14:24:15',1,'/bundles/cards/132011.png'),(483,38,4,3,12,'132012','To me! O my kinsfolk!','','<b>Action:</b> If you control at least 1 <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> hero, put a <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> ally from your discard pile into play under your control. Put that ally on the bottom of your deck at the end of the phase.','Out leapt the King under the Mountain, and his companions followed him. <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Tiziano Baracchi','16ae4f56-d8bb-41b8-a992-1da3b6ec1fdb','2016-03-17 00:34:43','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132012.png'),(484,38,4,6,13,'132013','The Lucky Number',NULL,'<b>Action:</b> Choose a character in play (other than Bilbo Baggins). Add Bilbo Baggins\' total [willpower], [attack], and [defense] to that character\'s [willpower], [attack], and [defense] respectively until the end of the phase.','\"I am the clue-finder, the web-cutter, the stinging fly. I was chosen for the lucky number.\"\r\n<cite>Bilbo Baggins, The Hobbit</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','65407141-e013-4d1c-8f70-4328e707d0cc','2016-03-17 00:34:50','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132013.png'),(485,38,3,1,14,'132014','Great Yew Bow','Item. Weapon.','Attach to a hero with the printed Ranged keyword. Restricted.\r\n<b>Combat Action:</b> Choose an enemy in the staging area. Exhaust Great Yew Bow and attached hero to make a ranged attack against that enemy. Declare attached hero as the attacker. No other attackers can be declared for this attack.',NULL,0,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Sara Biddle','833664a0-6bab-4e93-b5f1-88e7b6456569','2016-03-17 00:34:54','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132014.png'),(486,38,3,1,15,'132015','Black Arrow','Artifact. Item.','Limit 1 per deck. Attach to a hero with Ranged.\r\n<b>Response:</b> After attached hero declares an attack, add Black Arrow to the victory display to give attached hero +5 [attack] for this attack.','\"I have saved you to the last...\" <cite>Bard, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,3,1,'Melissa Findley','ae16236d-886e-4f65-9129-5ead1d373bfe','2016-03-17 00:35:01','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132015.png'),(487,38,3,2,16,'132016','Thrór\'s Key','Artifact. Item.','Attach to a hero.\n<b>Response:</b> After a location is added to the staging area, attach Thrór\'s Key to that location. While attached to a location, Thrór\'s Key gains: \"Treat attached location\'s printed text box as blank, except for traits.\"','\"The key that went with the map! Try it now while there is still time!\" <cite>Bilbo, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Eric Braddock','f4490261-317e-4e9e-9440-a5c58dcddcbf','2016-03-17 00:35:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132016.png'),(488,38,3,4,17,'132017','Expert Treasure-hunter','Skill.','Attach to a hero. Limit 1 per hero.\r\n<b>Response:</b> After attached hero quests successfully, name a card type and discard the top card of your deck. If the discarded card is the named type, take it into your hand.','\"Now I am a burglar indeed!\" –Bilbo, The Hobbit',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','2d550e71-f2a6-41f2-8aac-4533a965eb71','2016-03-17 00:35:16','2025-10-16 14:24:15',1,'/bundles/cards/132017.png'),(489,38,3,3,18,'132018','King Under the Mountain','Title.','Attach to a <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> hero.\r\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust King Under the Mountain to look at the top 2 cards of your deck. Add 1 to your hand and discard the other.','\"Long ago in my grandfather Thrór\'s time our family was driven out of the far North, and came back with all their wealth and tools to this Mountain on the map.\" <cite>Thorin, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','9152834a-5355-42ba-9592-1a3c1940d1a8','2016-03-17 00:35:20','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132018.png'),(490,38,5,5,19,'132019','Bilbo\'s Magic Ring','Artifact. Item. Ring.','Attach to Bilbo Baggins.\r\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Bilbo\'s Magic Ring and raise your threat by 1 to gain 1 [baggins] resource. (Limit once per round.)\r\n<b>Response:</b> After Bilbo Baggins exhausts to defend an attack, exhaust Bilbo\'s Magic Ring and raise your threat by 3 to cancel all damage from this attack.',NULL,1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Magali Villeneuve','9dd6bf3e-e090-4ebf-a056-765c94e8a199','2016-03-17 00:35:30','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132019.png'),(491,38,5,5,20,'132020','The Arkenstone','Artifact. Erebor. Item.','Attach to a hero.\r\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust The Arkenstone and raise your threat by X to lower by X the cost of the next ally you play this phase that matches the attached hero\'s sphere.','\"...the Heart of the Mountain; and it is also the heart of Thorin. He values it above a river of gold.\" <cite>Bilbo, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Mike Nash','ae774680-c6e9-49eb-96b8-fcdebe90b49d','2016-03-17 00:35:34','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132020.png'),(492,38,5,5,21,'132021','Mithril Shirt','Artifact. Erebor. Item.','Attach to Bilbo Baggins.\r\nAttached hero gets +1 [defense] and +1 hit point.','\"Mr. Baggins!\" he cried. \"Here is the first payment of your reward! Cast off your old coat and put on this!\" <cite>Thorin, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Tiziano Baracchi','12d51424-0edd-4977-9df1-5f6a7a5a96e1','2016-03-17 00:35:40','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132021.png'),(493,38,5,5,22,'132022','Thrór\'s Battle Axe','Artifact. Erebor. Item.','Attach to a hero. Restricted.\r\nAttached hero gets +2 [attack].\r\n<b>Response:</b> After attached hero attacks and destroys an enemy, deal 1 damage to another enemy engaged with you.','Royal indeed did Thorin look, clad in a coat of gold-plated rings, with a silver hafted axe... <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Tiziano Baracchi','857d6dc8-ba1e-4839-8e96-a8a0136a2302','2016-03-17 00:35:45','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132022.png'),(494,38,5,5,23,'132023','Thrór\'s Hunting Bow','Artifact. Erebor. Item.','Attach to a hero. Restricted.\r\nAttached hero gains Ranged.\r\nWhen making a ranged attack, attached hero gets +2 [attack].','Thorin seized a bow of horn and shot an arrow at the speaker. <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,3,'David Horne','7adc49c0-640d-4934-89c5-312ab584b77c','2016-03-17 00:35:49','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132023.png'),(495,38,5,5,24,'132024','Thrór\'s Golden Cup','Artifact. Erebor. Item.','Attach to a hero.\r\n<b>Action:</b> Add Thrór\'s Golden Cup to the victory display to draw 3 cards.','...the great golden cup of Thrór, two-handed, hammered and carven with birds and flowers whose eyes and petals were of jewels... <cite>The Hobbit</cite>',1,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,NULL,1,3,'Melanie Maier','ff7b0b9d-f8ae-4464-9db3-7205c5ae4db7','2016-03-17 00:36:01','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/132024.png'),(496,39,1,7,1,'141001','Frodo Baggins','Hobbit. Ring-bearer.','<b>Response:</b> Spend 1 [fellowship] resource and exhaust The One Ring to cancel the effect of an encounter card just revealed from the encounter deck. Shuffle that card back into the encounter deck and reveal another encounter card.','\"I will take the Ring,\" he said, \"though I do not know the way.\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,0,2,1,2,2,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Jake Murray','3217a119-6b86-47dd-b451-c5e45be3f874','2016-03-17 21:31:44','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141001.png'),(497,39,1,3,2,'141002','Sam Gamgee','Hobbit.','<b>Response:</b> After you engage an enemy with a higher engagement cost than your threat, ready Sam Gamgee. He gets +1 [willpower] +1 [attack] and +1 [defense] until the end of the round.','\"I\'m going with him...and if any of those Black Riders try to stop him, they\'ll have Sam Gamgee to reckon with\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,8,3,1,1,3,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Alexandre Dainche','4124136c-8c86-4f86-830c-94c8c76df161','2016-03-17 21:32:21','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141002.png'),(498,39,1,1,3,'141003','Merry','Hobbit.','Merry gets +1 [attack] for each Hobbit hero you control.\n<b>Response:</b> After Merry participates in an attack that destroys an enemy, ready another character that participated in that attack.','\"You can trust us to stick to you through thick and thin to the bitter end\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,6,2,0,1,2,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Alexandre Dainche','052b1f85-8b9c-4bb0-a735-bdbd5ac1b2c4','2016-03-17 21:32:56','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141003.png'),(499,39,1,4,4,'141004','Pippin','Hobbit.','Each enemy in play gets +1 engagement cost for each <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> hero you control.\n<b>Response:</b> After you engage an enemy with an engagement cost higher than your threat, draw a card.','\"We Hobbits ought to stick together, and we will\"\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,6,2,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Alexandre Dainche','ce96b767-c569-48b8-a998-d8009b0143c7','2016-03-17 21:33:16','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141004.png'),(500,39,1,2,5,'141005','Fatty Bolger','Hobbit.','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Fatty Bolger to choose an enemy in the staging area and raise your threat by that enemy\'s [threat]. Until the end of the phase, that enemy does not contribute its [threat]. (Limit once per round.)','\"I only hope that you do not need rescuing before the day is out\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,7,1,1,2,3,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Sebastian Giacobino','5d75d4dd-7300-43d7-87f2-963271c9c904','2016-03-17 21:33:29','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141005.png'),(501,39,2,3,6,'141006','Bill the Pony','Creature. Pony.','Cannot have attachments.\nLower the cost to play Bill the Pony by 2 if you control Sam Gamgee.\nEach <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> character gets +1 hit point.','\"He gave me a look as plain as Mr. Pippin could speak it: if you don\'t let me go with you, Sam, I\'ll follow on my own\" <cite>Sam Gamgee, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'2',NULL,1,1,0,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Christine Bian','1f7fc118-94a7-48a0-bd0c-9c15a36ddc23','2016-03-17 21:33:35','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141006.png'),(502,39,2,4,7,'141007','Barliman Butterbur','Bree.','If each hero you control has the <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> trait, damage from undefended attacks against you may be assigned to Barliman Butterbur.','\"But spooks or no spooks, they won\'t get in The Prancing Pony so easy.\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'2',NULL,1,0,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Owen William Weber','77f58774-86e7-4449-b31e-3833700b3e60','2016-03-17 21:33:42','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141007.png'),(503,39,2,1,8,'141008','Farmer Maggot','Hobbit.','<b>Response:</b> After Farmer Maggot enters play, deal 1 damage to an enemy engaged with you. (Deal 2 damage instead if that enemy\'s engagement cost is higher than your threat.)','\"It is lucky for you that I know you. I was going out to set my dogs on any strangers.\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'3',NULL,1,2,0,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Adam Lane','9d8ccd1a-48d3-4123-bcca-3c0ab88347ec','2016-03-17 21:33:51','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141008.png'),(504,39,4,1,9,'141009','Halfling Determination','','<b>Action:</b> Choose a <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> character. That character gets +2 [willpower], +2 [attack], and +2 [defense] until the end of the phase.','\"I have something to do before the end, and it lies ahead, not in the Shire. I must see it through, sir, if you understand me.\" <cite>Sam Gamgee, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','8e7e5c8d-0ea4-46df-ae38-d8d2fee7ca8b','2016-03-17 21:33:58','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141009.png'),(505,39,4,2,10,'141010','Smoke Rings','','<b>Action:</b> Reduce your threat by 1 for each <b><i>Pipe</i></b> you control. Each hero with a <b><i>Pipe</i></b> attachment gets +1 [willpower] until the end of the phase.','...he smoked and blew smoke-rings with the same vigour and delight...<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Lane Brown','9418c634-54c6-47de-9aae-798038a4a35b','2016-03-17 21:34:05','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141010.png'),(506,39,4,4,11,'141011','Take No Notice','','Lower the cost play Take No Notice by 1 for each <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> or <b><i>Ranger</i></b> hero you control.\n<b>Action:</b> Add 5 to each enemy\'s engagement cost until the end of the round.','...they made no noise that even hobbits would hear. Event the wild things in the fields and woods hardly noticed their passing. <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Adam Lane','768ae041-2d15-44a3-a928-62838536a160','2016-03-17 21:34:11','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141011.png'),(507,39,4,7,12,'141012','Frodo\'s Intuition',NULL,'<b>Action:</b> Each hero you control gets +1 [willpower] until the end of the round. Draw 1 card for each <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> hero you control.','\"I wonder if that is Gandalf coming after us\" said Frodo, but even as he said it, he had a feeling that it was not so... <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Winona Nelson','96350b97-5c68-4033-bb2f-4305696a7ae7','2016-03-17 21:35:17','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141012.png'),(508,39,3,1,14,'141014','Dagger of Westernesse','Artifact. Item. Weapon.','Restricted.\nAttach to a hero.\nAttached hero gets +1 [attack] (+2 [attack] instead if attacking an enemy with an engagement cost higher than your threat).','...these blades were forged many long years ago by Men of Westernesse: they were foes of the Dark Lord...\n<cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Sara Biddle','418e6de7-af19-4ea7-bfbe-2a02838c6de4','2016-03-17 21:40:40','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141014.png'),(509,39,3,2,15,'141015','Hobbit Pipe','Item. Pipe.','Attach to a <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> character. Limit 1 per character.\n<b>Response:</b> After your threat is reduced by an event card effect, exhaust Hobbit Pipe to draw a card.','But even the Dúnedain of Gondor allow us this credit: Hobbits first put it into pipes. Not even the Wizards first thought of that before we did. <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Mike Nash','9c455b1a-a2d4-44f7-a9d3-9a3134c21a2a','2016-03-17 21:40:47','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141015.png'),(510,39,3,4,16,'141016','Elf-stone','Artifact. Item.','Attach to the active location. Attached location gets +1 quest point.\n<b>Response:</b> After attached location leaves play as an explored location, the first player puts 1 ally into play from his hand.','\"It is a beryl, an elf-stone. Whether it was set there, or let fall by chance, I cannot say, but it brings hope to me\"\n<cite>Aragorn, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Sandara Tang','9bb32f2c-29fb-43ba-b7ba-2227b28f7b58','2016-03-17 21:40:54','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141016.png'),(511,39,3,3,13,'141013','Hobbit Cloak','Item.','Attach to a <b><i>Hobbit</i></b> hero. Limit 1 per hero.\nAttached hero gets +2 [defense] while defending against an attack by an enemy with an engagement cost higher than your threat.','In their dark cloaks they were invisible as if they all had magic rings. <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Alexandre Dainche','8e49ea86-375a-472e-b497-16a1164ae27f','2016-03-17 21:42:11','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/141013.png'),(512,40,1,7,1,'142001','Frodo Baggins','Hobbit. Ring-bearer.','<b>Response:</b> After Frodo Baggins exhausts to defend an attack, exhaust The One Ring and spend 1 [fellowship] resource to target the attacking enemy. Then, this attack deals no damage and each player raises his threat by 2.','\"But there is more about you now than appears on the surface.\" <cite>Bilbo, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,0,2,1,2,2,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Sebastian Giacobino','f9196cda-8f50-4cc5-9aad-1c56cb677bca','2016-03-17 21:44:59','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142001.png'),(513,40,1,5,2,'142002','Gandalf','Istari.','Play with the top card of your deck faceup. Once per phase, you may play the top card of your deck as if it was in your hand. When playing a card this way, Gandalf is considered to have the printed [leadership], [lore], [tactics], and [spirit] icons.','\"I am a servant of the Secret Fire, wielder of the flame of Anor.\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,NULL,14,3,3,3,5,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Matt Stewart','3e055edf-4540-4cf1-94ce-afbf5fc28f82','2016-03-17 21:45:15','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142002.png'),(514,40,2,3,3,'142003','Galadriel','Noldor. Noble.','At the end of the round, discard Galadriel from play.\n<b>Response:</b> After you play Galadriel from your hand, search the top 5 cards of your deck for an attachment of cost 3 or less and put it into play. Put the remaining cards back in any order.','',1,'3',NULL,3,0,0,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Sebastian Giacobino','3d09a998-9ad0-4b98-9c42-50c4226cc73b','2016-03-17 21:46:03','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142003.png'),(515,40,2,1,4,'142004','Boromir','Gondor. Warrior.','Boromir gets +2 [defense] while defending against an enemy with an engagement cost higher than your threat.\n<b>Response:</b> After Boromir takes any amount of damage, ready him.','',1,'4',NULL,1,3,1,4,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Chris Rahn','36b26228-1c01-4064-a109-d110e00d8e4b','2016-03-17 21:46:10','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142004.png'),(516,40,2,4,5,'142005','Elrond','Noldor. Healer.','At the end of the round, discard Elrond from play.\r\n<b>Response:</b> After Elrond enters play, choose one: heal all damage on a hero, discard a <b><i>Condition</i></b> attachment, or each player draws 1 card.',NULL,1,'3',NULL,3,2,3,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Allen Douglas','638638f0-8177-410a-bce8-9e2bbf5ad81f','2016-03-17 21:46:14','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142005.png'),(517,40,2,2,6,'142006','Bilbo Baggins','Hobbit.','<b>Response:</b> After Bilbo Baggins enters play, search your deck for a <b><i>Pipe</i></b> attachment and add it to your hand. Shuffle your deck.','\"Elves may thrive on speech alone, and Dwarves endure great weariness, but I am an old Hobbit, and I miss my meal at noon.\" <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'2',NULL,2,0,0,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Sebastian Giacobino','e02cc17b-80e4-4a8f-ba55-1df74aac816d','2016-03-17 21:46:46','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142006.png'),(518,40,4,5,7,'142007','Flame of Anor','Spell.','<b>Action:</b> Add Flame of Anor to the victory display and discard the top card of your deck to ready an <b><i>Istari</i></b> character you control. That character gets +X [attack] until the end of the phase where X is the discarded card\'s cost.','\"You cannot pass!\" <cite>Gandalf, The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,3,3,'Diego Gisbert Llorens','8a5ff815-56cf-4d5f-a649-a111e736a9f1','2016-03-17 21:47:31','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142007.png'),(519,40,3,5,8,'142008','Gandalf\'s Staff','Artifact. Item. Staff.','Attach to Gandalf. Restricted.\r\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Gandalf\'s Staff to (choose one): choose a player to draw 1 card, add 1 resource to a hero\'s resource pool, or discard a shadow card from a non-unique enemy.','...he held his staff aloft, and from its tip there came a feint radiance. <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',1,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Victor Maury','02e56cef-e78d-4dbd-bd4d-6ec43e4b1d2b','2016-03-17 21:47:37','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/142008.png'),(520,40,3,5,9,'142009','Wizard Pipe','Item. Pipe.','Attach to an <b><i>Istari</i></b> character. Limit 1 per character.\n<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Wizard Pipe to exchange a card in your hand with the top card of your deck.','...there was a long silence, broken only by the soft puffs of Gandalf\'s pipe, as he blew white smoke-rings out of the window. <cite>The Fellowship of the Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,