rd Elfhelm if he is still in play.','\"...my lord sends word that we must set ourselves in readiness; orders may come for a sudden move.\" <cite>The Return of the King</cite>',1,'4',NULL,1,2,2,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Javier Charro Martinez','0ff72c0f-a6d6-48d3-8781-1988a7e3ba11','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/146006.png'),(776,71,2,4,7,'146007','Elladan','Noldor. Ranger.','While Elrohir is in play, Elladan gets +2 [attack].\n<b.Response:</b> After you optionally engage an <b><i>Orc</i></b> enemy, ready Elladan.','...they rode often far afield with the Rangers of the North, forgetting never their mother\'s torment in the dens of the Orcs. <cite>The Return of the King</cite>',1,'3',NULL,2,1,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Jason Jenicke','51512531-0697-4005-9fb6-884da5b02f75','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/146007.png'),(777,71,2,2,8,'146008','Elrohir','Noldor. Ranger.','While Elladan is in play, Elrohir gets +2 [defense].\n<b.Response:</b> After you optionally engage an <b><i>Orc</i></b> enemy, ready Elrohir.','\"From the North we came with this purpose, and from Elrond our father we brought this very counsel.\" <cite>The Return of the King</cite>',1,'3',NULL,2,1,1,3,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Jason Jenicke','769dbf59-9e02-4750-9605-b1ad6c8783e2','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/146008.png'),(778,71,3,7,13,'146009','Orc Disguise','Item. Armor.','Attach to the <b><i>Ring-bearer</i></b>. Limit one per hero.\r\nWhile an <b><i>Orc</i></b> is making an enagement check with you, it gets +5 engagement cost.\r\n<b>Response:</b> After an <b><i>Orc</i></b> engages you, discard Orc Disguise. . Until the end of the round, that enemy cannot attack you.','\"Well, there you are, Mr. Frodo. A perfect little orc…\" <cite>Sam Gamgee, The Return of the King</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Borja Pindado','e4fd6941-6ced-4ddc-970d-a933ae7d5cb5','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/14600