e Ring</cite>',0,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Cristi Balanescu','1666b892-2182-41e6-87b6-e560f10701f6','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/31024.png'),(1241,51,1,2,25,'31025','Nori','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> After you play a <b><i>Dwarf</i></b> character from your hand, reduce your threat by 1.','\"Nori, at your service.\"\n<cite>Nori, The Hobbit</cite>',1,NULL,9,2,1,2,4,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Blake Henriksen','43aa19c5-4858-4217-8a16-826a52e8fb25','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/31025.png'),(1242,51,2,2,26,'31026','Kili','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> After you play Kili from your hand during the planning phase, search your deck for Fili and put him into play under your control. Then, shuffle your deck.','\"Let us join the throng!\"\n<cite>Kili, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'3',NULL,1,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Carmen Cianelti','168eb130-262e-4287-a70f-ad34397c1626','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/31026.png'),(1243,51,2,3,27,'31027','Fili','Dwarf.','<b>Response:</b> After you play Fili from your hand during the planning phase, search your deck for Kili and put him into play under your control. Then, shuffle your deck.','\"Fili is the youngest and still has the best sight.\"\n<cite>Thorin, The Hobbit</cite>',1,'3',NULL,1,1,1,2,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Carmen Cianelti','1f04497c-34ee-4d6b-a765-65103bc1ddd4','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/31027.png'),(1244,51,2,2,28,'31028','Zigil Miner','Dwarf.','<b>Action:</b> Exhaust Zigil Miner and name a number to discard the top 2 cards of your deck. If at least one of those cards has cost equal to the named number, choose a hero you control. For each card that matches the named number, add 1 resource to that hero\'s resource pool.','',0,'2',NULL,1,1,1,1,NULL,NULL,3,3,'Magali Villeneuve','d5f18486-1479-4e77-8ad4-a10d34a1a614','2025-10-15 22:13:12','2025-10-16 14:24:15',0,'/bundles/cards/31028.png'),(1245,51,2,2,29,'31029','Erebor Gua